descriptionHtml:
Location : Nr Dawnstar (Check Pictures) Fast travel enabled look for the camp icon 

Welcome to the Igloo Outpost living space mod,this igloo outpost works well as a mod 
for your new char or as another add-on to one of my other living space mods.Set in the
frozen iceland of dawnstar this mod gives you a igloo style player home with andother one
for storage & spare tent living area.The ship wreck adds to the scenery of the mod with
decorative fish racks and jetty/dock supplies,also there is some horkers to hunt.Nice little
mod with some good supplies & features worth a download,just give it a try.

Features 
************ 
Igloo fully furnished (Walk through banner over door) 
Crafting tables 
Cooking area 
Storage igloo 
Tent livng space fully furnished 
Ship Wreck & Treasure chest 
Fish racks & dock jetty with supplies 

Thanks for Looking...
author: EvilMrPumpkinsNexus
